1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,500
I found this 1954 photo

2
00:00:02,500 --> 00:00:04,500
of my grandfather.

3
00:00:04,500 --> 00:00:07,000
Look at the background.

4
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:10,000
He is in a park.

5
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:12,500
Behind him, stairs

6
00:00:12,500 --> 00:00:15,000
lead into thin air.

7
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:17,500
They stop at a

8
00:00:17,500 --> 00:00:20,000
solid brick wall.

9
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:24,000
I checked Google Street View.

10
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:27,500
The stairs are still there.

11
00:00:27,500 --> 00:00:31,000
They lead absolutely nowhere.

12
00:00:31,000 --> 00:00:34,000
Boost the brightness here.

13
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:36,500
See the figure

14
00:00:36,500 --> 00:00:39,000
standing beneath the steps?

15
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:41,400
They haven't moved in seventy years.